This appearance-settings.js file provides:
Key Features:
Theme System - 4 built-in themes (Sharingan, Mangeky≈ç, Rinnegan, Byakugan) + custom color picker
Sharingan Eye Configuration - Position, size, opacity, animation speeds, EMS pulse intensity
Translation Bubble Styling - 4 bubble styles, font selection, colors, sizing, smart positioning
Advanced Visual Effects - Scanlines, chakra particles, screen shake, chromatic aberration
Accessibility Options - Reduced motion, high contrast, large text, color blind modes
Live Preview - Real-time bubble preview that updates as you change settings
Technical Highlights:
Event-driven architecture with EventEmitter
Deep merge for settings management
Performance impact detection for heavy effects
Import/export functionality for settings backup
CSS variable generation for theme application
Comprehensive validation and error handling
The file integrates with the extension's config manager and communicates changes to background scripts via Chrome messaging.